PROJECT DESCRIPTION – Personalised Task Manager

Objective:
To provide a simple tool that helps users record tasks, update progress, and organise daily work in an
efficient way.

Problem Statement:
Users often forget tasks or lose track of progress. A simple personal task manager helps store tasks
and monitor progress easily.

Scope:
• User profile creation
• Password-based login
• Adding and storing tasks
• Updating task status
• Viewing data and status history

Target Users:
Students, professionals, and anyone needing a basic task tracker.

High-Level Features:
• Signup & Login
• Add Tasks
• Update Task Status
• Time-stamped status logs
• Data stored using text files
